Hey, partner.

357
00:43:09,879 --> 00:43:12,428
I think you'd better come inside.

358
00:43:19,430 --> 00:43:22,434
I can't worry about danger.

359
00:43:22,600 --> 00:43:24,728
This is something I must do.

360
00:43:36,072 --> 00:43:37,164
