361
00:43:41,577 --> 00:43:43,420
Now, where do you think
you're going?

362
00:43:43,579 --> 00:43:45,832
This is not your affair.

363
00:43:45,998 --> 00:43:49,468
Look, lady,
until I get my money,

364
00:43:49,627 --> 00:43:51,629
