397
00:45:45,201 --> 00:45:48,296
And today is just one of those
bad days, right?

398
00:45:48,454 --> 00:45:49,922
Ah.

399
00:45:51,666 --> 00:45:55,136
You know, I'm really happy
you came along, partner.

400
00:45:55,294 --> 00:45:59,720
That's very nice
of you to say.

