where is it?!

496
00:56:55,454 --> 00:56:57,377
I...

497
00:56:59,499 --> 00:57:03,299
I d-- I don't know.

498
00:57:03,462 --> 00:57:07,057
That's right.
You don't know, do you?

499
00:57:07,215 --> 00:57:09,309
(Sombra cackles)

500
00:57:09,468 --> 00:57:11,891
